headline: MicroStrategy, Coinbase Stocks Rise Alongside Bitcoin to Start 2025
summary: Shares of cryptocurrency-focused companies like Coinbase and MicroStrategy jumped Thursday morning ahead of the first trading session of the new year as Bitcoin also rose.
